<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186339>
    dc:description "FIGURES 28 – 30. Ptecticus infuscatus sp. nov., female terminalia in dorsal view (28), ventral view (29) and genital furca (30). Scale: 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/186339/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186337>
    dc:description "FIGURES 19 – 21. Ptecticus sarawakensis sp. nov., male terminalia. 19, lateral view. 20, epandrium, proctiger and cerci. 21, genital capsule, gonostyli and aedeagal complex. Scale: 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/186337/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186333>
    dc:description "FIGURES 4 – 7. Ptecticus bannapensis sp. nov., male terminalia. 4, lateral view. 5, epandrium, proctiger and cerci. 6, genital capsule and gonostyli. 7, aedeagal complex. Scale: 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/186333/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186341>
    dc:description "FIGURES 34 – 41. 34 – 35. Ptecticus aurifer (Walker), right wing (34) and medial part of costal margin (35). Scale: 5 mm (34); 1 mm (35). 36 – 37. Ptecticus australis Schiner, right wing (36) and medial part of costal margin (37). Scale: 5 mm (36). 38 – 39. Ptecticus cingulatus Loew, right wing (38) and medial part of costal margin (39). Scale: 5 mm (38); 1 mm (39). 40 – 41. Ptecticus proximus Rozkošný & Kovac (histrio group), right wing (40) and medial part of costal margin (41). Scale: 5 mm (40); 0.5 mm (41). See introduction for abbreviations." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/186341/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186342>
    dc:description "FIGURES 42 – 49. 42 – 43. Ptecticus longipennis (Wiedemann), right wing (42) and medial part of costal margin (43). Scale: 5 mm (42); 0.5 mm (43). 44 – 45. Ptecticus shirakii Nagatomi, right wing (44) and medial part of costal margin (45). Scale: 2 mm (44); 0.5 mm (45). 46 – 47. Ptecticus japonicus (Thunberg), right wing (46) and medial part of costal margin (47). Scale: 5 mm (46); 1 mm (47). 48 – 49. Ptecticus tricolor van der Wulp, right wing (48) and medial part of costal margin (49). Scale: 5 mm (48); 1 mm (49)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/186342/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186338>
    dc:description "FIGURES 25 – 27. Ptecticus elegans sp. nov., female terminalia in dorsal view (25), ventral view (26) and genital furca (27). Scale: 0.5 mm. For abbreviations see material and methods." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/186338/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186335>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11 – 14. Ptecticus indicus sp. nov., male terminalia. 11, lateral view. 12, epandrium, proctiger and cerci. 13, genital capsule and gonostyli. 14, aedeagal complex. Scale: 1.0 mm." ;
